  "title": "Part-Time Accounts Executive #79610",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Part-Time Accounts Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pandan Loop</li><li>Working Hours: 3 days per week (9.00am – 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $1,800</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage AP/AR: process invoices, payments, billing, and collections.</li><li>Perform bank reconciliations and maintain accurate cash records.</li><li>Handle payroll: prepare payslips and update payroll records.</li><li>Prepare tax schedules and support timely, accurate filings.</li><li>Liaise with auditors and banks; compile required documents.</li><li>Maintain organized filing and accounting documentation.</li><li>Support month-end close and full set of accounts reporting.</li><li>Perform other accounting-related duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Professional Certificate/NITEC in Finance, Accountancy, Bookkeeping, or equivalent.</li><li>At least 3 years of relevant experience in accounting.</li><li>Experience with MYOB and GST filing.</li><li>Able to work with minimal supervision.</li><li>Able to commit to two to three full days of on-site work each week.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79610 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
